23 - description:
• Eric Is Cool!
  • Litheon® advanced Lithium Ion 36V batteries allow more battery charges, longer run time and more power without adding significant weight
  • Uses the industry standard SDS-Plus® bit system to ensure the bit you need will be available
  • 1 solid bit capacity and 2-1/2 core bit capacity allow the user to tackle big jobs
  • The integral clutch helps to reduce torque reaction which helps prevent user fatigue
  • Operates in rotation only, rotary hammer or hammer only mode so you can tailor this Bulldog to your job
  • Generates 2.2 foot-pounds of impact force which is as much as many corded rotary hammers
  • Variable speed reversing trigger keeps the fine control in your hands
  • Tool-free bit changes with automatic bit locking, dust protection and maximum impact energy transfer rate give you the best of all worlds with speed and efficiency
  • Vario-LockTM positioning allows the user to rotate and lock a chisel into the right one of the 36 available positions, allowing the tool to be held for both the users comfort and at the best angle for the job
  • LitheonTM fast charger can charges 36V batteries to 80% of capacity in just 30 minutes
